    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process of passing a liquid or other material through a filter or porous medium in order to remove  or separate solid particles or impurities. May also refer to the process of passing an electrical signal or other signal through a filter to remove excess noise or undesired frequencies.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
